  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">SIM Card Registration via Blockchain Solution</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">FSD Uganda is providing technical assistance to Uganda Communications Commission (UCC) to support the development of a blockchain technology that would be adopted by Mobile Network Operators (MNOs). The objective of this intervention is to test whether this new technology would eliminate risks associated with SIM Identity theft with associated fraud from mobile money and linked mobile bank accounts</narrative>
  </description>
